" According to the China Earthquake Administration , as of 4 : 22 pm ( 0822 GMT ), the earthquake death toll has reached 100 , with more than 2 , 000 injured ," the China News Service reported Lushan authorities ' estimates of the injured ranged from 1 , 000 to 2 , 200 , while the provincial government said more than 10 , 000 homes were destroyed .